Frequent Questions
Can I upgrade from a yearly plan to the Lifetime plan?
You can upgrade at any time while still subscribed to one of our yearly plans by only paying the difference. This can be done from your Brizy account, under Account > Payments tab.
Can I use Brizy PRO to build sites for my paying clients?
Of-course, this is the exact purpose of Brizy PRO, giving you freedom to create websites for clients or for your own ventures.
Do you have a 100% money-back guaranteed policy?
Yes, we have a 30 days money-back guaranteed policy, no questions asked. If Brizy doesnt work for you, well refund the money as soon as possible. (We might ask for some feedback, but thats it.)
What happens if I dont continue the subscription after 1 year?

In case you no longer wish to continue your yearly subscription, the website(s) you have built with the PRO version of Brizy will continue to work,. You will remain on the latest version of the Brizy PRO plugin , but PRO features will be restricted and no more updates going forward.
What is the difference between Brizy WordPress & Cloud?

Brizy WordPress plugin needs to be installed on your own hosting plan inside WordPress CMS. Brizy Cloud is an all-inclusive platform that offers the same building tools as the WP version but also includes unlimited Cloud hosting.
